youth ENTREPRENEURSHIP 
Mrs. Karen Redman ( Kitchener Centre , Lib . ) : 
Mr. Speaker , I recently hosted the Prime Minister ' s caucus task force on youth entrepreneurship along with my colleagues from the Kitchener - Waterloo region . 
the task force spent its time in Kitchener speaking with young entrepreneurs , their mentors , service providers and members of the private sector . 
topics such as education , finances , resources and government support were all discussed . 
task force members visited a number of companies run by young entrepreneurs from the Kitchener - Waterloo area . 
we visited Joe Merlihan of the Woolwich Observer , Jen Herzog of Distinctive Stamp Design and John Rochetta of The Beat Goes On . 
the young entrepreneurs we met were dynamic , intelligent individuals who have used their talents in creative and unique ways . 
i commend the many young entrepreneurs from across the country who are working hard to make their dreams come true . 
